description: Almost 400 migrants rescued by three ships in the Mediterranean must be allowed to disembark, it says.
title: Migrant rescue: UN urges help as 200 taken off Banksy rescue boat
title_page: Migrant rescue: UN urges help as 200 taken off Banksy rescue boat - BBC News
maintext: The Maersk Etienne said it had been asked by the Maltese authorities to rescue the 27 people on board in early August but had not been allowed to bring them ashore. The Maltese government says the migrants were rescued outside Maltese waters and the tanker had never been asked to sail to Malta.
